2193 // where i and j are induction variables and c1 and c2 are loop invariants,
2194 // we can use the symbolic tests to disprove some dependences, serving as a
2195 // backup for the RDIV test. Note that i and j can be the same variable,
2196 // letting this test serve as a backup for the various SIV tests.
