2199 //  0 <= i <= N1 and some 0 <= j <= N2, where N1 and N2 are the (normalized)
2200 // loop bounds for the i and j loops, respectively. So, ...
2201 //
2202 // c1 + a1*i = c2 + a2*j
2203 // a1*i - a2*j = c2 - c1
